{{Quote|The marauders of Endor are creatures more akin to Imperial understanding, though pathetic in their own way. They revere their powerful technology, though they have forgotten how to use it.|[[Pfilbee Jhorn]]|<ref name="The Illustrated Star Wars Universe">''[[The Illustrated Star Wars Universe]]''</ref>}}
The '''Sanyassan Marauders''' were a band of [[Sanyassan/Legends|Sanyassan]] pirates who crash-landed on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]] in [[100 BBY/Legends|100 BBY]]. They allied with the [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Nightsister]] [[Charal]], who was also stranded on the planet. [[King/Legends|King]] [[Terak]] carved out a slice of Endor territory for himself, not far from [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]], and he made numerous attempts to find a ship that would take him and his people off Endor.

